title: Sleepless in Seattle (1993) (Tom Hanks, Meg Ryan)
description:
SLEEPLESS IN SEATTLE - 1993

IMDb Rating: 6.6
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108160/

  Tom Hanks plays Sam, left miserable by the death of his wife, with only his young son, Jonah (Ross Malinger), to console him. The consolation goes a bit far; Jonah rings up a radio talk show to say that his dad needs love. Many listeners melt with sympathy, none more so than Annie (Meg Ryan), in Baltimore, shortly to be married and none too happy about it.

  Starring: Tom Hanks, Meg Ryan, Bill Pullman, Ross Malinger, Rosie O'Donnell.

  Directed by: Nora Ephron.
